title: American Flagg v1
description:
This torrent includes issues 1-42 of American Flagg v1 from First Comics.

This was created written and drawn by Howard Chaykin, and eventually lived on beyond Howard&#039;s ability or interest to do everything on the book.

I have included American Flagg Special #1 as well.

There are 8 more issues to this series, but I haven&#039;t seen them scanned.

Thanks to the scanners and the original sources.

Please seed. Please enjoy.
